description: Kambi Group Plc provides sports betting solutions to business-to-customer operators. The company employs 903 full-time employees The company went IPO on 2014-06-02. The firm is engaged in the provision of managed sports betting services. The firm services consist of an offering from front-end user interface through to odds compiling, customer intelligence and risk management, built on in-house developed software. The firm's subsidiaries include Kambi Malta Limited, Kambi Spain plc, Sports Information Services Limited, Sports Information Services Limited, Kambi Services Limited, Kambi Services Limited, Global Technology & Sports Limited, Kambi Philippines Inc., Kambi Sports Solutions (Alderney) Limited, Kambi Australia Pty Ltd and Sports Analytics Services srl.
